==Abstract==
This TIP proposes to integrate [[https://github.com/sputn1ck/peerswap|PeerSwap]] protocol in trader clients to make submarine swaps between Liquid and Lightning Network.

==Motivation==
The purpose of this integration is to simplify the onboarding/offboarding to/from Liquid Network, with a faster deposit method compared to a Bitcoin pegin which takes 102 blocks to complete.

